<i>noun</i>: 형용 [형용], 묘사 [묘ː사] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>형용 [형용]</dt><br>
<dd>1. shape; figure; form</dd><br>
<dd>사물의 생긴 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>The appearance or shape of an object.</dd><br>
<dd>2. appearance; looks</dd><br>
<dd>사람의 생긴 모양이나 모습.</dd><br>
<dd>The appearance or features of a person.</dd><br>
<dd>3. description; depiction; portrayal</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 글, 동작 등으로 사람이나 사물의 모양을 나타냄.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of expressing the appearance of a person or thing through words, writing, gestures, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>묘사 [묘ː사]</dt><br>
<dd>description; portrayal; depiction</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 대상을 있는 그대로 자세하게 말이나 글로 표현하거나 그림으로 그림.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of giving a detailed account of a certain object in spoken or written words, or expressing it in paintings as it stands.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>